<P>
   BBO-CUBA-FANS (Havana) _ The scene. By James McKinley.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-DUKE-UCONN (St. Petersburg, Fla.) _ Only 40 minutes of
basketball are left before one team finishes a six-month blitz
through a hectic season as the best, before Duke completes the
decade with its third national championship or UConn snares its
first. By Jack Curry.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-DUKE-AVERY (St. Petersburg, Fla.) _ On William Avery, the
guard who makes Duke go. By Joe Drape.
</P>
<P>
   BKC-UCONN-MOORE (St. Petersburg, Fla.) _ On UConn's Ricky Moore,
