   INTERNET-MARKETPLACE (New York) _ During the next few months
there are likely to be a lot of delirious executives and employees
as more than a dozen of New York's Internet companies try to go
public. But it is the company founders who really have the right to
be delirious. By Lisa Napoli and Saul Hansell.
