   KOSOVO-ETHNIC-CLEANSING (Washington) _ Developments on
atrocities in Kosovo, described by officials as ``wholesale ethnic
cleansing'' and the worst humanitarian tragedy in Europe since
World War II. By the time NATO gets around to stopping the ethnic
cleansing, will Kosovo be empty, with Milosevic having achieved his
goal? By Jane Perlez.
