   ROCKET (Phoenix) The ``Rocket Boy'' of the Deer Valley School
District is quickly becoming a cult figure among space wonks around
the country. Thirteen-year-old David Silverstein, a seventh-grader
who was suspended for the rest of the school year for bringing a
