<DOCNO> NYT19990328.0195 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-28 20:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7315 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBO-CUBA-ORIOLES-450&AMP;     03-28 0487
