<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-28 22:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7405 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-REFUGEE-FLOOD-BOS &LR;      03-28 1558
